high_descs: Walk the length of the back of the sofa and hang a left at the white table, hang another left to stand at the round black coffee table in front of the sofa.
Pick up the red disk from the bottom shelf of the coffee table.
Turn to your left and walk in the direction of the sofa, hang a left to the cardboard box on the white table.
Place the red disk on the table to the left front side of the box.
Turn to your right and walk to the white shelf with the gold-colored disk on it.
Pick up the gold-colored disk from the shelf.
Turn to your left and walk to the cardboard box on the white table.
Place the gold-colored disk in front of the white plate to the right of the box.
anns.task_desc: Place a red and gold-colored disk near the cardboard box on the white table

high_descs: Proceed to end of couch on left, turn left, proceed to table on left. Turn left, go to table.
Remove red object from lower shelf of table.
Turn left, go to couch.  Turn left, go to table.
Place red object on table to left of remote.
Turn left, go ahead to shelves.
Pick up gold object from bottom shelf.
Turn around, proceed to table on right.  Turn right to face table.
Put gold object to the right of the remote and below the plate.
anns.task_desc: Move two objects to a table.

high_descs: move forwards past the couch on the left, then turn left and walk past the other side of the couch, then another left to walk over to the coffee table up ahead
grab a red disk off of the table there
turn around and walk over to the dining room table
place the disk on top of the dining room table
turn right and walk over to the end of the room where the white shelves are
take the golden disk off of the white shelves there
turn around and walk back over to the right side of the dining room table
place the gold disk on top of the dining room table
anns.task_desc: place two colored disks on top of the dining room table
